{{> header title="Update for your Transfer of Title request"}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px {{brand.layout.horizontalPadding}};">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Unfortunately, we’ve been unable to approve your application to transfer the service %%SERVICE_IDENTIFIER%% to your account.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          When assessing applications for plans, we rely on information from a number of sources, including the information you provide to us and the information received from credit reporting bodies. Our decision may be because you, or the business you applied on behalf of, don’t meet our current credit criteria.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          In your instance, it was partly or wholly based on the credit eligibility information we received from Illion and Equifax. You can obtain this information within 90 days free of charge using these contact details. It’s important to check the accuracy of your credit information as this may affect future applications for credit.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Illion</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          1300 734 806 (Personal)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          13 23 33 (Business)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          8.30am – 5.30pm AET (Monday – Friday)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Equifax</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          138 332 (Personal)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          1300 921 621 (Business)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          8.30am – 5.00pm AET (Monday – Friday)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you think that we may have failed to comply with Division 3 of Part IIIA of the Privacy Act or the Credit Reporting Code, you can make a complaint following our %%COMPLAINT_HANDLING_PROCESS%%.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you want to correct or access credit information about you, please visit our %%PRIVACY_POLICY%%.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px {{brand.layout.horizontalPadding}} 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
